x^2+y^2=(x+yi)(x-yi)=z^3=(a+bi)^3(a-bi)^3,
(1)x+yi=(a+bi)^3=a^3+3a^2bi-3ab^2-b^3i,
x=a^3-3ab^2,y=3a^2b-b^3,z=a^2+b^2.
(2)x+yi=(a+bi)^2(a-bi)=(a^2+b^2)(a+bi),
x=(a^2+b^2)a,y=(a^2+b^2)b,z=a^2+b^2
